{"text_id":58111,"tokens":["In"," India",","," you"," can"," claim"," a"," tax"," deduction"," on"," the"," interest"," paid"," on"," a"," personal"," loan"," under"," certain"," circumstances","."," To"," be"," eligible"," for"," this"," tax"," deduction",","," the"," personal"," loan"," must"," be"," taken"," for"," the"," purpose"," of"," higher"," education",","," construction"," or"," repair"," of"," a"," house",","," or"," for"," medical"," treatment",".","If"," the"," personal"," loan"," is"," taken"," for"," the"," purpose"," of"," higher"," education",","," the"," tax"," deduction"," is"," available"," under"," section"," ","8","0","E"," of"," the"," Income"," Tax"," Act","."," This"," deduction"," is"," available"," for"," a"," maximum"," period"," of"," ","8"," years"," or"," until"," the"," interest"," is"," fully"," paid"," off",","," whichever"," is"," earlier",".","If"," the"," personal"," loan"," is"," taken"," for"," the"," purpose"," of"," constructing"," or"," repairing"," a"," house",","," the"," tax"," deduction"," is"," available"," under"," section"," ","2","4"," of"," the"," Income"," Tax"," Act","."," The"," deduction"," is"," available"," for"," a"," maximum"," period"," of"," ","2","0"," years"," or"," until"," the"," interest"," is"," fully"," paid"," off",","," whichever"," is"," earlier",".","If"," the"," personal"," loan"," is"," taken"," for"," medical"," treatment",","," the"," tax"," deduction"," is"," available"," under"," section"," ","8","0","D"," of"," the"," Income"," Tax"," Act","."," The"," deduction"," is"," available"," for"," a"," maximum"," period"," of"," ","5"," years"," or"," until"," the"," interest"," is"," fully"," paid"," off",","," whichever"," is"," earlier",".","To"," claim"," these"," deductions",","," you"," must"," provide"," proof"," of"," the"," loan"," and"," the"," interest"," paid"," on"," it",","," such"," as"," a"," loan"," statement"," or"," interest"," certificate"," from"," the"," lender","."," You"